tadata endpoint bypasses the controller.\nSame pipeline, same validator: add Dhis2OAuth2ClientObjectBundleHook so\nevery OAuth2 client that flows through MetadataImportService is\nvalidated — reserved clientId squat, dangerous redirect URIs, bad grant\ntypes, and name defaulting all apply.\n\n- Moved OAuth2ClientAdminValidator from dhis-web-api to\n  dhis-service-core so both the controller (web-api -\u003e core) and the\n  hook (dxf2 -\u003e core) can reuse it.\n- Hook: validate() rejects create/rename-to-reserved / update of the\n  system registrar; preCreate/preUpdate applies name defaulting.\n- ConflictException from the validator is translated to an ErrorReport\n  on the hook's channel so the import pipeline surfaces it cleanly.\n\nDouble-execution on the REST path is harmless — all checks are\nidempotent.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"e97792af4331b2e653c1085200f6d12ee892dc83","tree_id":"76a86aad028cbcfcb38d31a79d2cb510be00daa5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T19:21:43Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.co